<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The <link linkend="_class_i_l3_app_msg_callback">IL3AppMsgCallback</link> class is an abstract base class that defines the interface for handling various CME iLink3 execution report messages and other related application level messages. </para>
</section>
